data.description: Welcome to this Charming ranch home located on a private street and situated on just over 1 acre to make your own. Minutes away from shopping, dining, Downtown Rock Hill and Cherry Park.  One owner home with a great open floor plan and open kitchen with plenty of natural sunlight coming through the beautiful plantation shutters. Single car garage with ample driveway parking and privacy. Schedule your showing today and make this home yours!
